Title: colspan-rowspan
------------------------------------

A column-span-only table:

| H1      | H2      | H3      |
|---------|---------|---------|
| This cell spans 3 columns |||
| Two-col span             || Single |

A row-span + col-span table:

| This header spans two       || Header A |
| columns and two rows       ^|| Header B |
|-------------|-----------:|----------|
| Cell A      | Cell B     | Cell C   |
